28:00.156 --> 28:01.157
- What does that mean?

28:01.201 --> 28:02.332
- For years, Keane's deputies

28:02.376 --> 28:03.507
have covered up the fact

28:03.551 --> 28:05.727
that he's suffering
from dementia.

28:05.771 --> 28:09.122
- Well, how bad is it?
I mean, good days, bad days?

28:09.165 --> 28:10.689
- Well, he thought
Carlos Hernandez played

28:10.732 --> 28:12.255
first base
for the '86 Mets, so...

28:12.299 --> 28:13.779
- Okay, well, what
about his deputies?

28:13.822 --> 28:16.520
Can't they step up?
'Cause we have three more

28:16.564 --> 28:18.218
rape kit hits
from Stanton's DNA.

28:18.261 --> 28:19.567
Plus an eye-witness.

28:19.610 --> 28:21.351
- Keane can't
even undo his tie,

28:21.395 --> 28:23.789
never mind a 16-year-old
double homicide.

28:23.832 --> 28:26.313
One of my former law
professors, he works

28:26.356 --> 28:27.662
in the Queens DA's office,

28:27.706 --> 28:29.403
he said he could try
to get Carlos a retrial.

28:29.446 --> 28:31.231
- Sorry to interrupt, Captain.

28:31.274 --> 28:33.450
Stanton's lawyer's here.
He needs a word.

28:35.452 --> 28:36.889
- [sighs]

28:36.932 --> 28:38.412
- My client will agree
to forcible touching

28:38.455 --> 28:39.587
on the girl from
Jacob Lawrence Houses.

28:39.630 --> 28:41.676
- He raped her.
- Says who?

28:41.720 --> 28:43.547
- She didn't see her attacker
and DNA on headphones?

28:43.591 --> 28:45.288
Probative of nothing.

28:45.332 --> 28:46.725
- We have a voice ID.

28:46.768 --> 28:48.596
- No eye witnesses,
only an ear witness.

28:48.639 --> 28:51.425
I'll convince the jury that
little Lupe is deaf and blind.

28:51.468 --> 28:54.558
- Little Lupe
is tougher than you think.

28:54.602 --> 28:56.822
- Juries love me
and they don't like cops.

28:56.865 --> 29:00.564
And that goes double for cops
who turned into prosecutors.

29:00.608 --> 29:02.392
They're gonna hate you.
- Well, maybe not...

29:02.436 --> 29:04.264
After they find out
your client's DNA

29:04.307 --> 29:05.569
was at three
different rape scenes.

29:05.613 --> 29:08.616
- And we have three
projects-strong girls,

29:08.659 --> 29:10.705
just like Lupe, who will
follow her to the stand.

29:10.749 --> 29:13.403
- We're going after
your client for all six rapes,

29:13.447 --> 29:15.754
including the Far Rockaway
rape and the double murder.

29:15.797 --> 29:17.451
- You're chasing
a 16-year-old murder case

29:17.494 --> 29:19.496
with two confessions?
And a district attorney

29:19.540 --> 29:21.368
who's playing poker
with tarot cards.

29:21.411 --> 29:22.891
- You wanna cut a deal?
Your client allocutes

29:22.935 --> 29:25.285
to the Hernandez murders
and maybe I can swing

29:25.328 --> 29:27.722
criminally negligent homicide
and rape two on the other six.

29:27.766 --> 29:29.593
- I ain't 'fessing
to no crack ho murders,

29:29.637 --> 29:31.508
and I ain't copping
to no pedo rapes.

29:31.552 --> 29:36.818
No short-eye pleas like those
'mos Torres and Hernandez did.

29:36.862 --> 29:38.777
- What do you know about that?

29:38.820 --> 29:42.781
- I got no idea how Carlos has
lasted 16 years in Green Haven.

29:42.824 --> 29:44.826
Everyone knows he's a fag.

29:44.870 --> 29:46.654
- All right, that's okay, Tim.
Look, we're done here.

29:46.697 --> 29:48.830
I'll be taking my client
back to processing.

29:52.225 --> 29:53.835
- Get him out of here.

29:53.879 --> 29:57.447
- You insist to murders
and child rapes,

29:57.491 --> 30:00.842
we'll go to the mat in my ring.

30:09.590 --> 30:11.679
- Don't let him get to you.

30:11.722 --> 30:14.334
- He didn't.
There's something Stanton said.

30:14.377 --> 30:16.510
Carlos told me
that he had an alibi

30:16.553 --> 30:19.426
for the night of the murders,
but he wouldn't talk about it.

30:19.469 --> 30:21.471
Now I know why.

30:24.344 --> 30:26.389
- A retrial?

30:26.433 --> 30:28.957
I can't have no DA
asking me questions, man.

30:29.001 --> 30:31.438
- Okay, Carlos...about that.

30:31.481 --> 30:33.396
- Could we get a few minutes?

30:40.882 --> 30:43.276
- Okay.

30:43.319 --> 30:46.279
Carlos, whatever you say here

30:46.322 --> 30:47.976
does not leave this room

30:48.020 --> 30:50.849
if you don't
want it to, I swear.

30:53.329 --> 30:55.897
Where were you that night?

30:59.379 --> 31:01.729
- I was at the beach.

31:01.772 --> 31:03.557
- What beach?

31:04.819 --> 31:06.952
- Plumb Beach in Brooklyn.

31:06.995 --> 31:09.737
- That's the boy-meets-boy
beach off the Belt Parkway?

31:09.780 --> 31:11.826
That Plumb Beach, right?

31:11.870 --> 31:15.699
- Okay, so you and Ricky
hooked up?

31:17.614 --> 31:19.442
- That was the first time.

31:21.314 --> 31:23.403
Beautiful night...

31:24.491 --> 31:26.362
Until I got home

31:26.406 --> 31:29.670
and I found my mommy
and Jacinta dead on the floor.

31:29.713 --> 31:31.324
- Listen, Carlos,

31:31.367 --> 31:34.631
a lot of people have come out
of the closet since then.

31:34.675 --> 31:36.720
Times have changed.
- Not in here.

31:36.764 --> 31:38.331
In here?

31:38.374 --> 31:41.377
Out of the closet
means into a casket.

31:41.421 --> 31:43.684
The other inmates
find out I'm gay?

31:43.727 --> 31:46.774
Gangs will turn me
into a Maytag.

31:46.817 --> 31:48.645
Washing socks and spit-shining.

31:48.689 --> 31:50.082
- Yeah, we get it.

31:50.125 --> 31:52.432
- I'd get bitched out
until I got the bug.

31:52.475 --> 31:54.564
Like Ricky.

32:00.570 --> 32:02.833
I know I'll never
walk again as a free man,

32:02.877 --> 32:05.706
but can I ask you a favor?

32:07.882 --> 32:10.102
- What's that, Carlos?

32:10.145 --> 32:13.409
- At night...
I still get the horrors,

32:13.453 --> 32:16.804
wondering where my mommy and
my little sister are buried.

32:16.847 --> 32:19.850
Thinking that they're in
an even worse place than me.

32:19.894 --> 32:22.027
I don't know...

32:22.070 --> 32:26.379
Potter's field
or unmarked graves...

32:26.422 --> 32:28.642
just lost souls.

32:30.687 --> 32:33.603
Find out where
my family's buried.

32:37.564 --> 32:39.348
- So Carlos and Ricky
were gay lovers

32:39.392 --> 32:42.134
and he can't give that alibi
because he'll be raped inside.

32:42.177 --> 32:43.744
- That's right.

32:43.787 --> 32:45.006
- And you brought
this happy news to me

32:45.050 --> 32:46.660
because...I'm gay.

32:46.703 --> 32:48.662
- No, but it doesn't hurt.

32:48.705 --> 32:50.969
I also know that you have
a justice gene buried under

32:51.012 --> 32:53.014
that jaded
Queens Boulevard veneer.

32:54.798 --> 32:56.452
- Look, maybe we can
get him protective custody

32:56.496 --> 32:57.758
while he's awaiting trial.

32:57.801 --> 32:59.499
- Protective custody
with his history?

32:59.542 --> 33:01.718
PTSD, depression...
he could suicide.

33:03.068 --> 33:05.679
Look, I'm--I'm asking you

33:05.722 --> 33:07.898
to help me spring
an innocent man.

33:07.942 --> 33:09.552
- Give me a night's sleep

33:09.596 --> 33:12.555
to figure out
what Voltaire would do...

33:16.995 --> 33:19.867
- Lupe would have to testify?
- I'm sorry, she would.

33:19.910 --> 33:21.782
- She's been
through enough already.

33:21.825 --> 33:23.566
And the lawyers?
They'll trick her.

33:23.610 --> 33:25.742
- No one can catch me in a lie
if I just tell the truth.

33:25.786 --> 33:27.048
- And she'd be prepped.

33:27.092 --> 33:28.528
We'd be with her
every step of the way.

33:28.571 --> 33:31.618
- Lupe,
you don't need to do this.

33:31.661 --> 33:33.837
- Mama, if he goes free,

33:33.881 --> 33:36.536
next time he might
just go after Gizelle.

33:39.234 --> 33:41.019
- Okay.

33:41.062 --> 33:43.630
- Thank you.
And thank you.

33:43.673 --> 33:46.763
Okay, we'll be in touch.
[phone ringing]

33:48.243 --> 33:50.550
Benson.

33:50.593 --> 33:52.769
Yes?

33:55.598 --> 33:57.644
What?

34:00.995 --> 34:02.997
When?

34:07.001 --> 34:09.612
Yeah, I'm on my way.

34:12.485 --> 34:14.704
- Captain?
Bad news?

34:14.748 --> 34:19.013
- Um...just have
a family thing.

34:19.057 --> 34:21.929
Um, can you get back
to the precinct on your own?

34:21.972 --> 34:23.104
- Of course.

34:23.148 --> 34:24.975
- Okay.

34:31.330 --> 34:31.547
.

34:31.591 --> 34:33.201
- That's him.

34:33.245 --> 34:35.421
That's my brother.

34:37.988 --> 34:40.643
- I'm sorry.

34:44.386 --> 34:46.432
- It was an OD?

34:46.475 --> 34:48.477
- Heroin laced with fentanyl.

34:50.392 --> 34:53.439
Found the body in a motel room,
no signs of foul play.

34:53.482 --> 34:55.571
- He was using...

34:55.615 --> 34:57.399
He told me that he was sober.

34:57.443 --> 34:59.967
- He was telling you the truth.

35:01.186 --> 35:03.013
If I had to guess,

35:03.057 --> 35:04.972
he'd been clean
for quite a while.

35:06.408 --> 35:08.541
- So it was not a suicide?

35:08.584 --> 35:11.109
- Dosage wasn't large enough.

35:12.414 --> 35:15.200
He just got his hands
on the wrong stuff.

35:15.243 --> 35:18.203
[somber music]

35:18.246 --> 35:22.511
