35:22.555 --> 35:24.470
- Okay...

35:24.513 --> 35:26.472
Well, thank you.

35:26.515 --> 35:28.604
- You two were close.

35:28.648 --> 35:31.999
- Not really, but, um...

35:33.653 --> 35:36.438
He was my only family.

35:36.482 --> 35:43.489
♪

35:55.501 --> 35:57.416
[breathing shakily]

35:57.459 --> 35:59.679
Simon...

36:14.215 --> 36:17.653
- Hey, the transport van
just dropped Carlos off

36:17.697 --> 36:19.220
outside of the courthouse.

36:19.264 --> 36:20.482
You wanna tell me
what's going on, Counselor?

36:20.526 --> 36:22.223
- Keane signed
the vacate order.

36:22.267 --> 36:24.530
- He did?
That's great.

36:24.573 --> 36:27.054
How'd you get
him to--to do that?

36:27.097 --> 36:29.187
- He may have thought
he was graciously signing

36:29.230 --> 36:31.493
a letter of recommendation
for my law school application.

36:31.537 --> 36:33.234
- All right, I didn't hear that

36:33.278 --> 36:35.236
and you did not say that,
but thank you.

36:35.280 --> 36:36.672
- Welcome to Queens.

36:36.716 --> 36:38.326
Let's go do this
before the ink dries

36:38.370 --> 36:40.546
or any of
his deputies find out.

36:45.203 --> 36:47.248
- It's all right.

36:47.292 --> 36:49.163
- Counselor,
you're representing

36:49.207 --> 36:50.773
the defendant,
Carlos Hernandez?

36:50.817 --> 36:52.253
- Yes, Your Honor.

36:52.297 --> 36:53.689
- I understand
you have a motion?

36:53.733 --> 36:55.213
- I do.

36:55.256 --> 36:56.431
Based on new
exculpatory evidence,

36:56.475 --> 36:57.693
defense moves to vacate

36:57.737 --> 36:59.217
the sentence
of Carlos Hernandez.

36:59.260 --> 37:01.088
- People?

37:01.131 --> 37:02.611
- The People believe there's
been a miscarriage of justice

37:02.655 --> 37:04.787
in this case, Your Honor.
Due to newly discovered

37:04.831 --> 37:06.789
DNA evidence implicating
a serial predator

37:06.833 --> 37:08.791
in these crimes,
the People ask that

37:08.835 --> 37:11.577
this verdict be vacated.

37:15.145 --> 37:18.453
- Mr. Hernandez, please stand.

37:21.151 --> 37:23.850
Carlos Hernandez,
I apologize on behalf

37:23.893 --> 37:26.896
of the state of New York
for your wrongful imprisonment

37:26.940 --> 37:30.726
that has cost you
16 years of your life.

37:30.770 --> 37:34.687
It is my duty today to vacate
this unjust conviction.

37:34.730 --> 37:38.212
[dramatic music]

37:38.256 --> 37:41.389
You are free to go.

37:41.433 --> 37:44.392
Bailiffs,
take off those chains.

37:44.436 --> 37:51.443
♪

38:07.720 --> 38:10.288
- You can walk like
a man now, Carlos.

38:13.247 --> 38:15.423
- A free man.

38:25.390 --> 38:27.740
- I don't understand.
Stanton's pleading guilty?

38:27.783 --> 38:29.307
- To two murders.

38:29.350 --> 38:31.265
- But not for Lupe's rape?

38:31.309 --> 38:33.876
- Well, either way, he's going
far away for a very long time.

38:33.920 --> 38:36.357
- And Lupe...
she won't have to testify.

38:36.401 --> 38:39.186
- Okay...that's good.

38:39.229 --> 38:41.406
- Can I give you a lift home?

38:41.449 --> 38:44.322
- Si, gracias.

38:53.331 --> 38:55.681
- Liv, are you okay?

39:03.384 --> 39:05.952
- No...

39:11.871 --> 39:15.918
I haven't told anyone,
but my brother, Simon...

39:18.704 --> 39:20.619
He died.

39:20.662 --> 39:22.795
- What?

39:22.838 --> 39:24.840
- He overdosed.

39:24.884 --> 39:26.842
[somber music]

39:26.886 --> 39:28.888
- I'm sorry.

39:28.931 --> 39:30.411
♪

39:30.455 --> 39:32.631
