39:44.425 --> 39:45.861
[breathes shakily]

39:45.905 --> 39:47.689
Is the last thing
that he heard?

39:51.432 --> 39:53.521
- You don't know that.

39:54.566 --> 39:56.481
The life he led...

39:56.524 --> 40:00.398
more likely it was...

40:01.747 --> 40:03.923
