40:19.765 --> 40:21.897
- [sniffles]

40:26.728 --> 40:28.687
That stone looks new.

40:28.730 --> 40:30.863
- Some people
read about your case.

40:30.906 --> 40:32.473
There was a GoFundMe.

40:32.517 --> 40:34.040
- A what?

40:34.083 --> 40:35.694
- Folks chipped in.

40:37.957 --> 40:40.046
- How can I ever thank you?

40:46.052 --> 40:49.447
[sniffles]

41:18.432 --> 41:18.606
.

41:18.650 --> 41:21.522
